Package model

Class AbstractEvent

java.lang.Object
model.AbstractEvent
All Implemented Interfaces:
Event
Direct Known Subclasses:
RecurringEvent, SingleEvent
public abstract class AbstractEvent extends Object implements Event
An abstract base class for events that provides common properties and methods.
